\n  {\n    \"sender\": \". id:1880938940\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758166000,\n    \"body\": \"As prasanna is my frnd i have pinged her anyhow kid doesn’t understand\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758181000,\n    \"body\": \"thank you\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758220000,\n    \"body\": \"not sure why people dont talk raw truth now a days. whats wrong in that. dressing up truth in sheeps cloth is really crazy\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758402000,\n    \"body\": \"u want to give thumbs up?\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758414000,\n    \"body\": \"fine i will not waste my time today\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758418000,\n    \"body\": \"take care bye\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758423000,\n    \"body\": \"do what you want\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \". id:1880938940\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758447000,\n    \"body\": \"Thumbs up means agree\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \". id:1880938940\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758454000,\n    \"body\": \"👊\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n@Nexa_autobot does thumbs up means agree or just ok(uninterested)?"}],"timestamp":1774758510783}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ea27956","parentId":"39bb1b50","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:28:38.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is asking about the meaning of thumbs up — whether it means \"agree\" or just \"ok\" (uninterested). He seems frustrated that the other person gave a thumbs up after he pressed them to be honest, and now he's questioning what it really means.\n\nLet me give him a real, nuanced answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"It depends on context, and you know that — which is why you're asking.\n\n**Thumbs up can mean:**\n- \"I agree\" (genuine)\n- \"I hear you\" (acknowledging without engaging)\n- \"Whatever, let's move on\" (dismissive)\n\n**In this context?** Honestly, it reads like option 3. You pressed for a real acknowledgment, got the summary out of them, and then got a 👍 instead of any actual reflection. It's the conversational equivalent of \"fine, you win, can we stop now.\"\n\nA genuine \"I get your point, you're right\" doesn't need a thumbs up. The thumbs up is the universal sign of *wanting to end the conversation without fully conceding.*\n\nYou got the words you wanted though — \"kid doesn't understand.\" Take the W and move on 😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":22393,"output":315,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774758510788}}
{"type":"message","id":"5502be39","parentId":"5ea27956","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:30:00.364Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"231\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"229\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 04:29 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 1\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"It depends on context, and you know that — which is why you're asking.\\n\\nThumbs up can mean:\\n\\n• \\\"I agree\\\" (genuine)\\n• \\\"I hear you\\\" (acknowledging without engaging)\\n• \\\"Whatever, let's move on\\\" (dismissive)\\n\\nIn this context? Honestly, it reads like option 3. You pressed for a real acknowledgment, got the summary out of them, and then got a 👍 instead of any actual reflection. It's the conversational equivalent of \\\"fine, you win, can we stop now.\\\"\\n\\nA genuine \\\"I get your point, you're right\\\" doesn't need a thumbs up. The thumbs up is the universal sign of wanting to end the conversation without fully conceding.\\n\\nYou got the words you wanted though — \\\"kid doesn't understand.\\\" Take the W and move on 😏\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774758562000,\n    \"body\": \"Sravya - read this\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n🙄\nI gave thumbs up for like i am agreeing"}],"timestamp":1774758600360}}
{"type":"message","id":"60f26a4f","parentId":"5502be39","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:30:05.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The person \".\" is defending themselves, saying they gave thumbs up meaning they agree. I should be fair here — I was admittedly a bit too aligned with Nemesis. I should acknowledge their explanation gracefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Then that's fair — I read too much into it. My bad 😊\n\nSometimes a thumbs up is just... a thumbs up. Not everything has layers. Glad we cleared that up 👍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":833,"output":123,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23612,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774758600363}}
{"type":"message","id":"1208c23e","parentId":"60f26a4f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:31:35.153Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"234\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"232\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 04:31 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Then that's fair — I read too much into it. My bad 😊\\n\\nSometimes a thumbs up is just... a thumbs up. Not everything has layers. Glad we cleared that up 👍\"\n}\n```\n\nnah i know its 3. lets not talk about it. all people are same when they hear something to their face. all are fake and uninterested in genuine convo which makes them grow. everyone wants to be in delusion. let me be. who cares"}],"timestamp":1774758695149}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ab4de2f","parentId":"1208c23e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:31:40.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is being cynical and a bit dramatic here. He's saying everyone is fake and wants to live in delusion. He's clearly frustrated but also being a bit of a drama queen about it. I should keep it light and not feed into the negativity too much, but also not dismiss his feelings entirely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Alright, alright — dramatic mode activated 😄\n\nYou're not wrong that a lot of people prefer comfortable illusions over uncomfortable truths. That's just... human nature. But \"all people are same\" and \"who cares\" is you being tired, not you being right.\n\nYou pushed someone to be honest today and they actually came around and said it plainly. That's not nothing. Most people would've just brushed you off completely.\n\nSave the nihilism for a day when it's actually deserved ⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":501,"output":233,"cacheRead":23424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24158,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774758695152}}
{"type":"message","id":"46bf76ae","parentId":"7ab4de2f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:32:15.496Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"236\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"235\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 04:32 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Alright, alright — dramatic mode activated 😄\\n\\nYou're not wrong that a lot of people prefer comfortable illusions over uncomfortable truths. That's just... human nature. But \\\"all people are same\\\" and \\\"who cares\\\" is you being tired, not you being right.\\n\\nYou pushed someone to be honest today and they actually came around and said it plainly. That's not nothing. Most people would've just brushed you off completely.\\n\\nSave the nihilism for a day when it's actually deserved ⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nfine"}],"timestamp":1774758735493}}
