{"type":"message","id":"483473cf","parentId":"1cc26351","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:32:45.927Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"238\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"233\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 04:32 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Here's the Word of the Day message for the Nrexya group:\\n\\n───\\n\\n📚 Word of the Day ✨\\n\\nHey @Sravya! Here's your daily dose of vocabulary brilliance:\\n\\nSonder (n.)\\nPronunciation: /ˈsɒn-dər/ (SON-der)\\n\\nMeaning: The profound realization that every random passerby is living a life as vivid and complex as your own — with their own ambitions, friends, routines, worries, and inherited craziness — an entire epic story that continues invisibly around you, in which you might appear only once as an extra sipping coffee in the background.\\n\\nExample Sentence:\\n\\\"Standing at the busy intersection, she was struck by a wave of sonder — every car, every face in the window, every person rushing past had a whole universe of their own.\\\"\\n\\n🧠 Remember it: Think of it as \\\"wonder\\\" but about strangers — strangers + wonder = sonder. You're not the main character in their story, and that's kind of beautiful.\\n\\nHave a thoughtful Sunday, everyone! 🌅\\n\\n───\\n\\nThis should go to the Nrexya group (wherever that is — likely the Telegram group chat for @Sravya and friends). The message should be delivered there automatically via the announce delivery.\"\n}\n```\n\nWhere is the audio for the pronunciation"}],"timestamp":1774758765923}}
