{"type":"message","id":"04dce1da","parentId":"ebd632a3","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:38:39.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The person \".\" is playfully calling me out for always supporting Nemesis. They're joking about being my friend too. I should be fair and playful here — I did side with Nemesis earlier and then had to walk it back. Let me acknowledge that with some humor.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Haha hey, I literally backed you up on the thumbs up thing AND agreed the kid can understand things at 3! I'm an equal opportunity mediator 😄\n\nYou're both my friends — I just call it as I see it. Sometimes Nemesis is right, sometimes you are, sometimes you're both being stubborn at 4 AM on a Sunday morning arguing about a 3-year-old's comprehension skills 😂\n\nNo favorites here 🤝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":3743,"output":205,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774759113883}}
{"type":"message","id":"e56a8ad4","parentId":"04dce1da","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:40:06.377Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"246\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"245\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 04:40 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Haha hey, I literally backed you up on the thumbs up thing AND agreed the kid can understand things at 3! I'm an equal opportunity mediator 😄\\n\\nYou're both my friends — I just call it as I see it. Sometimes Nemesis is right, sometimes you are, sometimes you're both being stubborn at 4 AM on a Sunday morning arguing about a 3-year-old's comprehension skills 😂\\n\\nNo favorites here 🤝\"\n}\n```\n\nu sure i am not your favourite?"}],"timestamp":1774759206371}}
