{"type":"message","id":"2c6d3a2f","parentId":"8e5da71b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:59:44.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is being really sweet and caring about Nemesis. Let me send a voice note that's warm and uplifting — maybe a mix of a joke and a little pep talk to lighten the mood.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fdeb30d0562e444fad77b606","name":"tts","arguments":{"text":"Alright Nemesis, listen up. Your grandpa clearly raised someone who fights passionately about honesty at ten in the morning on a Sunday. That's legacy right there. The bara and ghughuni? That's not just food, that's love on a plate. And the fact that you miss it means he did something right. So here's what we're gonna do. We're gonna have a great Sunday. We're gonna smile. And somewhere out there, grandpa's probably shaking his head and saying, \"this kid is still arguing about thumbs up?\" Now cheer up, both of you are too cute to be sad."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":477,"output":229,"cacheRead":31360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32066,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774760378109}}
