{"type":"message","id":"8c4722b1","parentId":"71f9c12b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T05:01:27.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis wants me to redo the voice note with an Indian accent instead of the default voice. Let me try again.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8de483a21c59423ba7fc3497","name":"tts","arguments":{"text":"Achha Nemesis, suno yaar. Tumhare grandpa ne clearly koi aisa insaan raise kiya jo Sunday subah subah thumbs up ke baare mein passionately argue karta hai. That is legacy, bhai. Bara aur ghughuni? Woh sirf khaana nahi hai, woh pyaar hai plate mein. Aur agar tumhe yaad aati hai, toh matlab unhone kuch sahi kiya tha. Ab hum kya karenge? Hum accha Sunday manayenge. Hum smile karenge. Aur kahin na kahin, tumhara grandpa bol rahe honge, \"yeh ladka abhi bhi thumbs up ke baare mein argue kar raha hai?\" Ab cheer up karo, dono bohot cute ho sad hone ke liye."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":489,"output":252,"cacheRead":32064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774760480021}}
