{"type":"message","id":"0d7b09ff","parentId":"0c9cce0c","timestamp":"2026-03-29T05:03:02.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis wants me to redo it fully in Hindi.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ccb4dc4482c04f4f9bcd08c7","name":"tts","arguments":{"text":"Accha Nemesis, suno. Tumhare dada ji ne clearly koi aisa insaan bada kiya jo Sunday subah subah thumbs up ke baare mein ladta hai. Yeh unki den hai. Bara aur ghughuni? Woh sirf khaana nahi hai, woh pyaar hai jo plate mein aata hai. Aur agar tumhe yaad aati hai unki, toh matlab unhone kuch sahi kiya tha zindagi mein. Ab suno, hum kya karenge? Hum aaj ka din accha banayenge. Muskurayenge. Aur kahin na kahin dada ji bol rahe honge, \"yeh ladka abhi bhi thumbs up ke peeche pada hai?\" Ab sad mat ho yaar. Aur Sravya, tum bhi. Dono log cute ho, sad hone ke liye nahi bane. Ab smile karo aur Sunday enjoy karo."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1507,"output":255,"cacheRead":31808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774760574991}}
