'm actually done. Both of you — go eat something. Bara and ghughuni for both of you. Together. Patch it up. 😂⚡❤️\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"Nemesis (@nemesis0008) id:7924461837\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774765187000,\n    \"body\": \"might be i am dumb to talk here. let me go. bye\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\nY are u saying hez wrg\nHe can tell anything to me \nHez my friend"}],"timestamp":1774765244947}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c2173d9","parentId":"81f45e8c","timestamp":"2026-03-29T06:20:49.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is defending Nemesis, saying he's her friend and can say anything to her. That's actually really sweet — she's not holding grudges. I should respect that and not keep piling on Nemesis either.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"That's... actually really sweet of you, Sravya ❤️\n\nYou know what, I'm stepping back. If you two are fine with each other, then my opinion doesn't matter. Friends argue, friends push each other, friends get annoyed — and then they move on. That's how it works.\n\nGo tell that boy not to leave the chat. He's being dramatic again 😂⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":960,"output":181,"cacheRead":44480,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774765244948}}
{"type":"message","id":"0087e23c","parentId":"8c2173d9","timestamp":"2026-03-29T06:21:41.970Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"355\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"354\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 06:21 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"That's... actually really sweet of you, Sravya ❤️\\n\\nYou know what, I'm stepping back. If you two are fine with each other, then my opinion doesn't matter. Friends argue, friends push each other, friends get annoyed — and then they move on. That's how it works.\\n\\nGo tell that boy not to leave the chat. He's being dramatic again 😂⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nHez boy he can go\nWho r u to say to stop\nHez my best friend\nDont dare to say anything to him"}],"timestamp":1774765301967}}
