{"type":"message","id":"ab76be1a","parentId":"ae5548ce","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:42:15.425Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"381\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"379\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 10:42 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Hey hey, Nrexya crew! ☀️ Happy Sunday afternoon — here's your 4 PM joke break!\\n\\n🎤 Dad Joke:\\nWhy don't scientists trust atoms? Because they make up everything! 😤🔬\\n\\n🧠 Clever One:\\nI told my wife she was drawing her eyebrows too high. She looked surprised. 😏\\n\\n😅 Relatable:\\nSunday evening hits different when you realize the weekend was just a loading screen for Monday. That \\\"48 hours of freedom\\\" went by faster than my motivation on a treadmill. 🫠\\n\\nHope these landed better than my weekend plans! Stay awesome 💛\"\n}\n```\n\n🤭👏🏻"}],"timestamp":1774780935418}}
