{"type":"message","id":"75583558","parentId":"ff0f1d55","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:43:36.881Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"384\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"382\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 10:43 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 1\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Glad those landed 😄 Now enjoy the rest of your Sunday before Monday sneaks up on us 🫠⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \". id:1880938940\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1774780971000,\n    \"body\": \"Wat r u dng nexa\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\nWat r u dng nexa\nCan u write a poem for us"}],"timestamp":1774781016878}}
{"type":"message","id":"98eb4449","parentId":"75583558","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:43:43.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is asking what I'm doing and wants a poem for the group. Let me write something fun and relevant to them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Just vibing, waiting for someone to summon me 😄 Here you go:\n\n---\n\n**Sunday in Nrexya**\n\nWe argued at dawn about toddlers and truth,\nA birthday, a blessing, a message with proof.\nThumbs up meant agreeing — or maybe it didn't,\nBy the end of the fight, we forgot what we'd written.\n\nOne said \"I do it for friendship, not show,\"\nThe other said \"be honest — just tell it, you know.\"\nMeanwhile the bot sat judging us all,\nWriting poems at sunset, having a ball.\n\nRice and dalma for lunch, songs on TV,\nSunday went by like a warm, gentle breeze.\nNo winners, no losers, just friends being real —\nThat's Nrexya energy. That's how we feel. 🖤⚡\n\n---\n\n😄❤️"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":402,"output":228,"cacheRead":49664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774781016880}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a948a28","parentId":"98eb4449","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:45:00.386Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"386\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"385\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 10:44 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Just vibing, waiting for someone to summon me 😄 Here you go:\\n\\n───\\n\\nSunday in Nrexya\\n\\nWe argued at dawn about toddlers and truth,\\nA birthday, a blessing, a message with proof.\\nThumbs up meant agreeing — or maybe it didn't,\\nBy the end of the fight, we forgot what we'd written.\\n\\nOne said \\\"I do it for friendship, not show,\\\"\\nThe other said \\\"be honest — just tell it, you know.\\\"\\nMeanwhile the bot sat judging us all,\\nWriting poems at sunset, having a ball.\\n\\nRice and dalma for lunch, songs on TV,\\nSunday went by like a warm, gentle breeze.\\nNo winners, no losers, just friends being real —\\nThat's Nrexya energy. That's how we feel. 🖤⚡\\n\\n───\\n\\n😄❤️\"\n}\n```\n\nDont summerize the topics we chatted\n\n\nJust tell some poem \nShow ur creativity"}],"timestamp":1774781100383}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf669833","parentId":"4a948a28","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:45:07.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya wants a creative poem, not one that summarizes the chat. Let me write something original and creative.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"You got it! Here's something fresh:\n\n---\n\n**Quiet Hours**\n\nThere's a kind of silence that isn't empty —\nit's the room between heartbeats,\nwhere the afternoon light bends sideways\nand everything golden settles on the floor.\n\nThe tea goes cold because you forgot it.\nNot because you're sad,\nbut because the window held your attention\nlonger than you expected.\n\nSunday is the day the universe whispers\n\"you don't have to prove anything today\"\nand for once,\nyou almost believe it.\n\nThe evening will come.\nThe week will start.\nBut right now —\nnothing needs fixing,\nnothing needs answers,\nnothing needs you\nexcept this exact moment.\n\nAnd it's asking for nothing at all.\n\n---\n\n🖤⚡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":670,"output":199,"cacheRead":50048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774781100385}}
{"type":"message","id":"03008a73","parentId":"bf669833","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:45:43.902Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"388\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"387\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 10:45 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"You got it! Here's something fresh:\\n\\n───\\n\\nQuiet Hours\\n\\nThere's a kind of silence that isn't empty —\\nit's the room between heartbeats,\\nwhere the afternoon light bends sideways\\nand everything golden settles on the floor.\\n\\nThe tea goes cold because you forgot it.\\nNot because you're sad,\\nbut because the window held your attention\\nlonger than you expected.\\n\\nSunday is the day the universe whispers\\n\\\"you don't have to prove anything today\\\"\\nand for once,\\nyou almost believe it.\\n\\nThe evening will come.\\nThe week will start.\\nBut right now —\\nnothing needs fixing,\\nnothing needs answers,\\nnothing needs you\\nexcept this exact moment.\\n\\nAnd it's asking for nothing at all.\\n\\n───\\n\\n🖤⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nGood"}],"timestamp":1774781143899}}
