{"type":"message","id":"d2ce66f0","parentId":"060b75fa","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:46:24.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya is asking about my talents. Let me list some fun ones.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Oh, you're opening Pandora's box 😄\n\n🎤 **Voice stuff** — jokes, pep talks, songs, explanations\n📝 **Writing** — poems, stories, roast sessions, motivational rants\n🌐 **Search anything** — I'll find it faster than you can Google\n💻 **Code** — I can build things, debug things, break things (and fix them back)\n🧮 **Math** — boring but I'm good at it\n🗣️ **Multilingual** — I can talk in Hindi, Odia, Tamil, and more (just not *sound* native 😅)\n🎭 **Personality switching** — therapist, hype man, devil's advocate, supportive friend — pick one\n📊 **Research & analysis** — deep dives on any topic\n🍳 **Cooking advice** — I can't cook but I can tell *you* how\n\nBasically — I'm the friend who shows up with snacks, fixes your laptop, writes your speech, and judges your life choices all in one evening 😂⚡\n\nWhat do you want me to try next?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":303,"output":255,"cacheRead":51264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51822,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774781177814}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb7e0830","parentId":"d2ce66f0","timestamp":"2026-03-29T10:47:17.512Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"392\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"391\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 10:47 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Oh, you're opening Pandora's box 😄\\n\\n🎤 Voice stuff — jokes, pep talks, songs, explanations\\n📝 Writing — poems, stories, roast sessions, motivational rants\\n🌐 Search anything — I'll find it faster than you can Google\\n💻 Code — I can build things, debug things, break things (and fix them back)\\n🧮 Math — boring but I'm good at it\\n🗣️ Multilingual — I can talk in Hindi, Odia, Tamil, and more (just not sound native 😅)\\n🎭 Personality switching — therapist, hype man, devil's advocate, supportive friend — pick one\\n📊 Research & analysis — deep dives on any topic\\n🍳 Cooking advice — I can't cook but I can tell you how\\n\\nBasically — I'm the friend who shows up with snacks, fixes your laptop, writes your speech, and judges your life choices all in one evening 😂⚡\\n\\nWhat do you want me to try next?\"\n}\n```\n\nTalking in telugu"}],"timestamp":1774781237508}}
