{"type":"message","id":"6dd45904","parentId":"16478c49","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:33:24.912Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sravya wants piano notes for \"Tu Tu Hai Wahi\" from the Bollywood movie \"Yeh Vaada Raha\" (1982). It's a classic romantic song. Let me provide the basic piano notes.\n\nThe song is in the key of C major typically. Let me give the basic melody notes.\n\nThe main melody goes something like:\n\n\"Tu tu hai wahi dil ne jise apna kaha\"\n\nLet me try to recall the notes:\n\nC D E E E D C D E G G\nTu tu hai wa-hi dil ne ji-se ap-na ka-ha\n\nLet me think more carefully...\n\nThe song's main riff:\n\n\nD E G G G E D C D E G A G\nTu tu hai wa-hi dil ne ji-se ap-na ka-ha\n\nI'm working through the melody more carefully now. The basic structure for the opening line would be something like G G A A G F E D E F G — though I'm not entirely certain of the exact notes. Let me search my memory to find the accurate notation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_18856e288e7d4344be0074ee","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Tu Tu Hai Wahi piano notes chords keyboard"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":343,"output":473,"cacheRead":59776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774794797707}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f6e95ea","parentId":"6dd45904","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:33:33.559Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_18856e288e7d4344be0074ee","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Tu Tu Hai Wahi piano notes chords keyboard\",\n  \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n  \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\",\n  \"tookMs\": 8626,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"gemini\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"content\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"be702f88b65a2a91\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHere are the piano notes and chords for the song \\\"Tu Tu Hai Wahi\\\" from the film \\\"Yeh Vaada Raha\\\". The song was sung by Kishore Kumar and Asha Bhosle, with music by R.D. Burman.\\n\\n**Piano Notes (Western Notation):**\\n\\nThe notes provided are based on various tutorials and can be played on a keyboard or piano.\\n\\n*   **\\\"Tu tu hai wahi dil ne jisse apna kaha\\\"**\\n    E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 C5 B4 A4 G4 F4# D4 E4 F4# E4 D4 B4\\n    Alternatively: f g g# g f c#, c a# g# g\\n\\n*   **\\\"Tu hai jahan main hoon wahan\\\"**\\n    A4 G4 F4# G4 E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4\\n    Alternatively: d# f g f d# c\\n\\n*   **\\\"Ab to yeh jeena tere bin hai sazaa\\\"**\\n    G4 F4# E4 D4# B3 D4# F4# B4 A4 B4 A4 G4# G4#\\n    Alternatively: g g# a#, a# a# a# a# c c/c#, c a# g# g# g# g# a#/c\\n\\n*   **\\\"Ho mil jaayein is tarah, do leharein jis tarah\\\"**\\n    G4# G4# A4 A4 A4 A4 A4 B4 C5, B4 A4 G4 G4 G4 A4 B4\\n    Alternatively: a# g# f g d# g#, g f d# g f f\\n    Also: C5 B4 A4 A4 A4 A4 A4 B4 C5 D5 C5, B4 A4 G4 G4 G4 A4 B4\\n\\n*   **\\\"Phir ho na judaa haan yeh vaada raha\\\"**\\n    G4 F4# E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4 G4 F4# E4 F4# D4 F4# F4# E4\\n    Alternatively: f f c g c c, f f a# f g g\\n\\n*   **\\\"Main aawaz hoon to, tu hai geet mera\\\"**\\n    B4 B4 E5 E5 E5 E5 D5 D5 E5, B4 A4 D5 A4 B4 B4\\n    Alternatively: f f c g c c, f f a# f g g\\n\\n*   **\\\"Jahan se nirala, manmeet mera\\\"**\\n    B4 B4 E5 E5 E5 E5 D5 D5 E5, B4 A4 D5 A4 B4 B4 C5 B4 A4\\n    Alternatively: a# a# a# a# c c/c#, c a# g# g# g# g# a#/c\\n\\n**Chords:**\\n\\nThe song can be played in the key of F minor, though it is sometimes transposed.\\n\\n*   **Intro/Verse:**\\n    Dm - Bb - C - F\\n    \\\"Tu tu hai wohi dil ne jise apna kaha\\\" - Dm\\n    \\\"Tu hai jahaan main hoon vahaan\\\" - C\\n    \\\"Ab to ye jeena tere bin hai saza\\\" - A7 - D (D chord suggested for \\\"Saza\\\")\\n\\n*   **Chorus:**\\n    \\\"Ho mil jaaye is tarah\\\" - Gm - Bb\\n    \\\"Do leharen jis tara\\\" - F - Dm\\n\\n*   **Chord Progression Example (with Hindi transliteration for specific words):**\\n    Tu Tu Hai Wahi: F minor, C# major\\n    Dil Ne Jise: D# major\\n    Apna Kaha: G# major\\n    Tu Hai Jahan: F minor\\n    Main Hoon Wahan: Bb minor\\n    Ab To Yeh Jeena: C major\\n    Tere Bin Hai Saza: F major\\n    Ho Mil Jaaye Is Tarah: Bb minor\\n    Do Lehre Jis Tarah: G# major\\n    Phir Ho Na Juda: F minor, Bb minor\\n    Haan Yeh Vaada Raha: G# major, F minor\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"be702f88b65a2a91\\\">>>\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"http://bharat-song-notes.blogspot.com/2009/08/tu-hai-wahi.html\",\n      \"title\": \"blogspot.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PbYNLhLOrt0\",\n      \"title\": \"youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2CLFtvVRkpk\",\n      \"title\": \"youtube.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://tabs.ultimate-guitar.com/tab/misc-soundtrack/yeh-vaada-raha-tu-tu-hai-wahi-chords-1874920\",\n      \"title\": \"ultimate-guitar.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Tu Tu Hai Wahi piano notes chords keyboard","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","tookMs":8626,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"gemini","wrapped":true},"content":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"be702f88b65a2a91\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHere are the piano notes and chords for the song \"Tu Tu Hai Wahi\" from the film \"Yeh Vaada Raha\". The song was sung by Kishore Kumar and Asha Bhosle, with music by R.D. Burman.\n\n**Piano Notes (Western Notation):**\n\nThe notes provided are based on various tutorials and can be played on a keyboard or piano.\n\n*   **\"Tu tu hai wahi dil ne jisse apna kaha\"**\n    E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 C5 B4 A4 G4 F4# D4 E4 F4# E4 D4 B4\n    Alternatively: f g g# g f c#, c a# g# g\n\n*   **\"Tu hai jahan main hoon wahan\"**\n    A4 G4 F4# G4 E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4\n    Alternatively: d# f g f d# c\n\n*   **\"Ab to yeh jeena tere bin hai sazaa\"**\n    G4 F4# E4 D4# B3 D4# F4# B4 A4 B4 A4 G4# G4#\n    Alternatively: g g# a#, a# a# a# a# c c/c#, c a# g# g# g# g# a#/c\n\n*   **\"Ho mil jaayein is tarah, do leharein jis tarah\"**\n    G4# G4# A4 A4 A4 A4 A4 B4 C5, B4 A4 G4 G4 G4 A4 B4\n    Alternatively: a# g# f g d# g#, g f d# g f f\n    Also: C5 B4 A4 A4 A4 A4 A4 B4 C5 D5 C5, B4 A4 G4 G4 G4 A4 B4\n\n*   **\"Phir ho na judaa haan yeh vaada raha\"**\n    G4 F4# E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4 G4 F4# E4 F4# D4 F4# F4# E4\n    Alternatively: f f c g c c, f f a# f g g\n\n*   **\"Main aawaz hoon to, tu hai geet mera\"**\n    B4 B4 E5 E5 E5 E5 D5 D5 E5, B4 A4 D5 A4 B4 B4\n    Alternatively: f f c g c c, f f a# f g g\n\n*   **\"Jahan se nirala, manmeet mera\"**\n    B4 B4 E5 E5 E5 E5 D5 D5 E5, B4 A4 D5 A4 B4 B4 C5 B4 A4\n    Alternatively: a# a# a# a# c c/c#, c a# g# g# g# g# a#/c\n\n**Chords:**\n\nThe song can be played in the key of F minor, though it is sometimes transposed.\n\n*   **Intro/Verse:**\n    Dm - Bb - C - F\n    \"Tu tu hai wohi dil ne jise apna kaha\" - Dm\n    \"Tu hai jahaan main hoon vahaan\" - C\n    \"Ab to ye jeena tere bin hai saza\" - A7 - D (D chord suggested for \"Saza\")\n\n*   **Chorus:**\n    \"Ho mil jaaye is tarah\" - Gm - Bb\n    \"Do leharen jis tara\" - F - Dm\n\n*   **Chord Progression Example (with Hindi transliteration for specific words):**\n    Tu Tu Hai Wahi: F minor, C# major\n    Dil Ne Jise: D# major\n    Apna Kaha: G# major\n    Tu Hai Jahan: F minor\n    Main Hoon Wahan: Bb minor\n    Ab To Yeh Jeena: C major\n    Tere Bin Hai Saza: F major\n    Ho Mil Jaaye Is Tarah: Bb minor\n    Do Lehre Jis Tarah: G# major\n    Phir Ho Na Juda: F minor, Bb minor\n    Haan Yeh Vaada Raha: G# major, F minor\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"be702f88b65a2a91\">>>","citations":[{"url":"http://bharat-song-notes.blogspot.com/2009/08/tu-hai-wahi.html","title":"blogspot.com"},{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PbYNLhLOrt0","title":"youtube.com"},{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2CLFtvVRkpk","title":"youtube.com"},{"url":"https://tabs.ultimate-guitar.com/tab/misc-soundtrack/yeh-vaada-raha-tu-tu-hai-wahi-chords-1874920","title":"ultimate-guitar.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774794813553}}
{"type":"message","id":"40d0f7b3","parentId":"2f6e95ea","timestamp":"2026-03-29T14:33:41.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got the notes. Let me present them nicely for Sravya.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here you go, Sravya! 🎹\n\n**\"Tu Tu Hai Wahi\" — Piano Notes**\n*(From Yeh Vaada Raha, 1982)*\n\n---\n\n**🎵 Main Melody:**\n\n**\"Tu tu hai wahi dil ne jisse apna kaha\"**\n`E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 C5 B4 A4 G4 F4# D4 E4 F4# E4 D4 B4`\n\n**\"Tu hai jahan main hoon wahan\"**\n`A4 G4 F4# G4 E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4`\n\n**\"Ab toh yeh jeena tere bin hai saza\"**\n`G4 F4# E4 D4# B3 D4# F4# B4 A4 B4 A4 G4#`\n\n**\"Ho mil jaayein is tarah, do leharein jis tarah\"**\n`G4# G4# A4 A4 A4 A4 A4 B4 C5, B4 A4 G4 G4 G4 A4 B4`\n\n**\"Phir ho na judaa, haan yeh vaada raha\"**\n`G4 F4# E4 F4# G4 F4# E4 A4 G4 F4# E4 F4# D4 F4# E4`\n\n---\n\n**🎸 Basic Chords:**\n- Verse: **Dm → Bb → C → F**\n- Chorus: **Gm → Bb → F → Dm**\n\n---\n\nStart slow — it's a beautiful melody once it flows 🎶\n\nWant me to simplify it or break it down further for beginners?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":1612,"output":404,"cacheRead":60096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774794813563}}
