rt with Arrow — Cupid's arrow. Falling in love. Classic crush symbol.\\n• 💝 Heart with Ribbon — Gift of love. Valentine's vibes. \\\"Here, take my heart.\\\"\\n• 💞 Revolving Hearts — Mutual love, two hearts in sync. Relationship energy.\\n• 💕 Two Hearts — Love between two people. Romantic, gentle, paired.\\n• 🫶 Heart Hands — Appreciation, gratitude, \\\"sending love.\\\" Non-romantic warmth.\\n\\n───\\n\\nQuick cheat sheet:\\n\\n• ❤️ Romance | 💛 Bestie | 💙 Trust | 💜 Compassion | 🖤 Edgy cool | 🤍 Pure | 🧡 Warmth\\n\\nThere you go — now you can heart with precision 😄⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nThank u for info bro"}],"timestamp":1774795594456}}
