spoils it\\n• Stays fresh for up to a year if stored properly\\n• Adjust salt based on mango sourness 🥭\\n\\nServe with steamed rice or roti. Enjoy, sis! 😋⚡\"\n}\n```\n\nYeah thank u nexa"}],"timestamp":1774842129176}}
